1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,432
Tom walked into a library and said, “I’d like a burger, fries, and a large cola.”

2
00:00:07,432 --> 00:00:13,891
The librarian stared at him and whispered, “Sir, this is a library.”

3
00:00:13,891 --> 00:00:15,959
Tom looked embarrassed.

4
00:00:15,959 --> 00:00:23,032
He leaned closer and whispered, “Sorry… I’d like a burger, fries, and a large cola.”

5
00:00:23,032 --> 00:00:25,243
The librarian sighed.

6
00:00:25,243 --> 00:00:27,455
“We don’t serve food here.”

7
00:00:27,455 --> 00:00:29,775
Tom nodded seriously.

8
00:00:29,775 --> 00:00:31,195
“That’s okay.”

9
00:00:31,195 --> 00:00:35,423
“Then I’ll just eat the book about sandwiches.”

10
00:00:35,423 --> 00:00:37,923
“Is it in the delicious section?”

11
00:00:37,923 --> 00:00:45,212
The librarian said, “No, but your joke definitely belongs in the fiction section.”
